trans-unit.source: Enables Windows authentication with client application services.
trans-unit.target: 클라이언트 응용 프로그램 서비스와 함께 Windows 인증을 사용 하도록 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: You can use client application services to validate users by using Windows authentication.
trans-unit.target: Windows 인증을 사용 하 여 확인 하므로 사용자가 클라이언트 응용 프로그램 서비스를 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: To enable Windows authentication, you configure your application to use the ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider class.
trans-unit.target: Windows 인증을 사용 하려면 응용 프로그램 ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider 클래스를 사용 하도록 구성 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Configure Client Application Services](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은 참조 [하는 방법: 클라이언트 응용 프로그램 서비스 구성](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)합니다.

trans-unit.source: After configuration, you can validate users by calling the `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: 을 구성한 후 호출 하 여 사용자가 확인할 수 있습니다는 `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드.</xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method internally calls the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드를 내부적으로 호출 된 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method automatically authenticates the current user and sets the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object that contains the current <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드는 현재 사용자를 자동으로 인증을 설정 하 고는 `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성을 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>현재 <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> 를 포함 하는 개체</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> is configured for your application, you can use the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object to retrieve user role information from the roles service.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>구성 된 응용 프로그램에 대해 사용할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>역할 서비스에서 사용자 역할 정보를 검색할 개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>

trans-unit.source: You can retrieve a reference to the current ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider instance through the `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: 통해 현재 ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider 인스턴스에 대 한 참조를 검색할 수 있습니다는 `static` <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성.</xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.Provider%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can use the membership provider reference to call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method directly.
trans-unit.target: 멤버 자격 공급자 참조를 사용 하 여 호출 하 여 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드를 직접.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, you will need the membership provider reference to call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A> method, which is not available in the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider> base class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A> <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider>기본 클래스</xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipProvider> 에서 사용할 수 없는 메서드</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.Logout%2A> 를 호출 하는 멤버 자격 공급자 참조 해야 합니다는 또한

trans-unit.source: Logs out the user.
trans-unit.target: 사용자를 로그 아웃 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For users authenticated through client application services, the `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is set to a <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> object that enables access to the configured role service.
trans-unit.target: 클라이언트 응용 프로그램 서비스를 통해 인증 된 사용자에 대 한는 `static` <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성이로 설정 되는 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal>구성된 된 역할 서비스에 액세스할 수 있도록 하는 개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.ClientRolePrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The Logout method resets the <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> property to a <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal> object that contains the current <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.
trans-unit.target: 로그 아웃 메서드는 <xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A>속성을 <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal>현재 <xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity>.</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsIdentity> 를 포함 하는 개체</xref:System.Security.Principal.WindowsPrincipal> </xref:System.Threading.Thread.CurrentPrincipal%2A> 를 다시 설정

trans-unit.source: After you call this method, you can no longer retrieve roles for the user through the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> class.
trans-unit.target: 이 메서드를 호출 하면 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider>클래스</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientRoleProvider> 를 통해 사용자에 대 한 역할을 더 이상 검색할 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: To reauthenticate the current user, call the <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: 현재 사용자를 다시 인증 하도록 호출는 <xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>메서드.</xref:System.Web.ClientServices.Providers.ClientWindowsAuthenticationMembershipProvider.ValidateUser%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
